entally distinct cell populations were found to co-cluster based on gene expression and were manually separated as follows: MAIT_2 were separated from the co-clustered VD2 and CD8_Tem populations based on co-expression of SLC4A10 and TRAV1-2; VD1_Eff were separated from the co-clustered CD8_IFNG population based on lack of expression of abTCR chains.  CTV data was similarly processed.
